        "summary": "We should pray for all people\u2014Christ is our Mediator\u2014Women should dress modestly\u2014Women are blessed in childbearing and are admonished to continue in faith, charity, and holiness.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "I exhort therefore, that, first of all, supplications, prayers, intercessions, and giving of thanks, be made for all men;",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 79,
                        "end": 82
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For kings, and for all that are in authority; that we may lead a quiet and peaceable life in all godliness and honesty.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Governments; Kings, Earthly.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 9
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Peace; Peacemakers.",
                        "start": 75,
                        "end": 84
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Citizenship.",
                        "start": 85,
                        "end": 89
                    },
                    {
