                        "start": 30,
                        "end": 38
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 12
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Who gave himself a ransom for all, to be testified in due time.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Self-Sacrifice.",
                        "start": 4,
                        "end": 8
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Job 33:24. TG\u00a0Jesus Christ, Atonement through; Jesus Christ, Redeemer.",
                        "start": 19,
                        "end": 25
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Heb. 9:16 (16\u201317); D&C 135:5.",
                        "start": 41,
                        "end": 50
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Whereunto I am ordained a preacher, and an apostle, (I speak the truth in Christ, and lie not;) a teacher of the Gentiles in faith and verity.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Called of God.",
                        "start": 15,
                        "end": 23
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Preaching.",
                        "start": 26,
                        "end": 34
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Cor. 9:1. TG\u00a0Apostles.",
                        "start": 43,
                        "end": 50
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Rom. 9:1.",
                        "start": 86,
                        "end": 89
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Acts 9:15.",
                        "start": 113,
                        "end": 121
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0truth.",
                        "start": 135,
                        "end": 141
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
